title: Minister Congratulates Australia’s Sporting Legends (Premier of Victoria)
text: ( Source : Premier of Victoria ) Australia's sporting legends have been recognised at the 31st Sport Australia Hall of Fame Induction and Awards Gala dinner held once again in Melbourne , the sporting capital of the world. Minister for Sport
